elements.name: Verify search results has multiple countries before refinement

steps.name: I am on the Home Page
I enter "Test" in the Job Title search box
I should see search results from multiple locations
I click on the Country category
I should see search results where the location is "Netherlands" only

elements.name: Search for Sales jobs and refine by Germany

steps.name: I am on the Home Page
I click on Search for Job Title text field
I select Sales among Job Categories
the Sales Category count and the search results count should match
I click on the Country category
I select the "Germany" checkbox in Sales Page
the Sales Category count and the search results count should match
